NOORCHAIN’s total supply — 299,792,458 NUR — is permanently capped and cannot be altered.
A fixed supply provides:
•	Predictability: institutions and partners can plan decades ahead.
•	Transparency: no discretionary minting or hidden inflation.
•	Economic stability: rewards are distributed at a controlled pace.
•	Ethical orientation: the protocol protects participants from dilution.
