15.3 Curator Ethical Code
Curators must operate under strict ethical guidelines:
•	act with neutrality and fairness
•	validate only legitimate actions
•	avoid conflicts of interest
•	protect the integrity of NOORCHAIN
•	maintain transparency in validation
•	respect privacy and legal boundaries
•	never validate actions for personal benefit
Curators are ethical stewards, not economic actors.
